{"id":624425,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/12/【图说天朝】微信上讨论《当代政治与经济》被封/","date":"2019-12-16T09:29:09Z","modified":"2019-12-16T09:29:09Z","title":"【图说天朝】微信上讨论《当代政治与经济》被封群","content":"<p>12月15日，网传一则“微信申诉图”，自称是传播专业大学生的网友，因在微信上和组员讨论《当代政治与经济》触发关键词而遭到封禁。作者自称“怀着爱国热情”，进行正常的教学讨论，质问腾讯为何“不去封禁真正危害国家安全的内容”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/ELzG1PCUYAErp5l.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-624426\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/ELzG1PCUYAErp5l.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"820\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/ELzG1PCUYAErp5l.jpeg 1125w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/ELzG1PCUYAErp5l-183x300.jpeg 183w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/ELzG1PCUYAErp5l-624x1024.jpeg 624w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/ELzG1PCUYAErp5l-768x1260.jpeg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/ELzG1PCUYAErp5l-936x1536.jpeg 936w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/12/ELzG1PCUYAErp5l-1080x1772.jpeg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n","author":972,"categories":[18271,38895,38912,39486],"tags":[28724,9249,34718,22995,10008]}